create(address[],uint256[],address,addre.details: Grant creation function. May be called by grantors, grantees, or any other relevant party.

params._amounts: Respective allocations for each Grantee (must follow sort order of _grantees).
params._contractExpiration: (Optional) Block number after which payouts must be complete or anyone can trigger refunds.
params._currency: (Optional) If null, amount is in wei, otherwise address of ERC20-compliant contract.
params._extraData: Support for extensions to the Standard.
params._fundingExpiration: (Optional) Block number after which votes OR funds (dependant on GrantType) cannot be sent.
params._manager: (Optional) Multisig or EOA address of grant manager.
params._targetFunding: (Optional) Funding threshold required to release funds.
